Hello! My name is Paige Fitzpatrick. I am the owner of Fizpatrick’s Little Boutique. 
We offer custom boutique clothing, tees for everyone and more! ♥️ We have been in business since 2019 and we are adding new products every week! 
I MOSTLY POST IN THE VIP FACEBOOK GROUP - join the group to see all available items to order!
If you have any questions I’m always reachable by email. fitzpatrickslittleboutique@yahoo.com
